    <br/>
    "Uh-uh."
    <br/>
    "nuh-uh."
    <br/>
    "um-no."
    <br/>
    "uh-no."
    <br/>
    "no, no, no...not that."
    <br/>
    <br/>
    The "wave-no" sign is a way to express such concepts.
